Before compiling:
-----------------
Make sure you have g++ and the Boost C++ libraries installed. On Ubuntu Linux, the packages g++ and libboost-dev are what you need.

How to compile:
---------------
./configure
make

How to install:
---------------
su
make install

How to compile using the configure front-end:
---------------------------------------------
./setup.sh
make

Typical configuration:
----------------------
CFLAGS="-Wall -O2 -DNDEBUG" ./configure --prefix=/usr/local

Debug configuration:
--------------------
CFLAGS="-Wall -g" ./configure
